# Equality Saturation Theory Exploration à la Carte

This file is a transition-time build anchor for the public page.
The canonical publication record and assets live in `pubs/2023-oopsla-enumo/`.

Edit `pubs/2023-oopsla-enumo/publication.json` for structured publication
data, keep the abstract/BibTeX/assets in the same directory, and use
`pubs/2023-oopsla-enumo/extra.dj` for any rare page-specific extra content.
